@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<div class="text-center mt-5 p-5 rounded shadow" style="background-color:#f8f9fa;">
    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Welcome to LifePlanner System</h1>
    <p class="lead mt-3">
        Plan your daily tasks, organize your life, and stay productive every day.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h3 class="mb-3 text-primary">Main Features</h3>
    <ul class="list-group">
        <li class="list-group-item">✅ Create, edit and delete personal tasks</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">✅ Organize events and reminders</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">✅ Clean and simple user interface</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">✅ Designed for everyday productivity</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="card shadow border-0">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title text-success mb-3">About LifePlanner System</h3>
            <p class="card-text">
                LifePlanner System is a smart personal organization platform designed to help users
                manage their daily responsibilities in a simple and efficient way. The system allows
                users to plan tasks, track goals, set reminders, and organize their daily routines
                in one centralized place.
            </p>
            <p class="card-text">
                The main idea of LifePlanner is to reduce stress caused by poor time management and to
                help users stay focused, productive, and consistent in their everyday life. It is
                suitable for students, professionals, and anyone who wants better control over their time.
            </p>
            <p class="card-text">
                With a clean and user-friendly interface, LifePlanner provides an easy way to visualize
                daily plans, deadlines, and priorities, making it easier to achieve both short-term and
                long-term goals.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h3 class="mb-3 text-primary">How LifePlanner helps you in real life</h3>
    <div class="row g-3">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">For students</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Students can use LifePlanner to track homework, exam dates, project deadlines
                        and study sessions, so they never forget an important task again.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">For working people</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Employees and freelancers can plan meetings, daily tasks and personal goals,
                        keeping both work and private life balanced in one place.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">For personal growth</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        LifePlanner can be used to build habits, track progress on goals and stay
                        motivated by having a clear overview of what needs to be done each day.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container mt-5 mb-4">
    <h3 class="mb-3 text-warning">Future features</h3>
    <p>
        In the future, LifePlanner can be extended with notifications, calendar integration,
        mobile support and sharing plans with friends or family members.
        The goal is to make LifePlanner a simple, but powerful assistant for daily life.
    </p>
</div>